    <item>
      <title>卢比奥出席巴拿马驱逐仪式，凸显特朗普对移民问题的关注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/rubio-watches-panama-deport-colombians-to-underscore-trump-s-migration-focus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国务卿马尔科·卢比奥监督了从巴拿马飞往哥伦比亚的驱逐航班，这对于美国高级外交官来说是一次不寻常的举动，旨在强调唐纳德·特朗普总统对移民问题的关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/rubio-watches-panama-deport-colombians-to-underscore-trump-s-migration-focus</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 16:32:25 GMT</pubDate>
