    <item>
      <title>德国梅尔茨承诺限制移民并恢复增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/germany-s-merz-promises-to-limit-migration-and-restore-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国大选中保守党领跑者弗里德里希·梅尔茨誓言，尽管遭到公众抗议，但仍将坚持推行备受争议的限制移民计划，并恢复德国疲弱的经济的增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/germany-s-merz-promises-to-limit-migration-and-restore-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 16:23:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥财政部长 Sheinbaum 称关税将推迟一个月</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/mexico-s-sheinbaum-says-tariffs-delayed-for-a-month</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普周一与美国贸易代表克劳迪娅·辛鲍姆进行会谈后同意将对墨西哥征收 25% 的关税推迟一个月，这对于濒临贸易战的邻国来说是一个戏剧性的转变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/mexico-s-sheinbaum-says-tariffs-delayed-for-a-month</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 15:26:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国总理冒着遭到谴责的风险强行通过预算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/french-premier-forces-through-budget-risking-no-confidence-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总理弗朗索瓦·贝鲁周一绕过议会下院，强行通过了 2025 年预算法案，而宪法中规定可能会引发不信任投票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/french-premier-forces-through-budget-risking-no-confidence-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 15:22:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
